{"name":"Critical Failure","img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","description":"Roll the outcome of a fumble","results":[{"_id":"F0MTS17tSXz2TgRO","type":0,"text":"Wrong Target: GM chooses a new target near the intended one. Roll to hit with a base chance of 10-, applying any appropriate difficulty modifiers, to see if the new target is struck.  (Default 3)","weight":1,"range":[1,2],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":1,"rangeH":2},{"_id":"l4jfIx0N7s7VuMnR","type":0,"text":"Off Balance: The attacker suffers a penalty of -3 on defense until they regain their balance on their next turn.","weight":1,"range":[3,4],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":3,"rangeH":4},{"_id":"3F6xMiP7DQJF5PfX","type":0,"text":"Leg Strain: The attacker suffers 1 Hit of damage* to a randomly selected leg. See Called Shots (see 4.14.2).  (Default 3)","weight":1,"range":[5,6],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":5,"rangeH":6},{"_id":"kCld7AR1Hcbk9a9q","type":0,"text":"Left An Opening: The target immediately gets a free action, which they may use to strike at their attacker or for any other purpose.  (Default: 19)","weight":1,"range":[7,8],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":7,"rangeH":8},{"_id":"7fQl1t8QmjRpKKHx","type":0,"text":"Muscle Strain: The attacker strains themself. Roll the attacker’s Base HTH damage, add the pushing bonus if they were pushing, divide by 2, and round up. Their protection applies against this damage, and they may roll with it.","weight":1,"range":[9,10],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":9,"rangeH":10},{"_id":"5sSpJffw336uE7dg","type":0,"text":"Arm Strain: The attacker suffers 1 Hit of damage* to a randomly selected arm. See Called Shots (see 4.14.2).  (Default: 15)","weight":1,"range":[11,12],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":11,"rangeH":12},{"_id":"fzefqKJ3CUF0NwyV","type":0,"text":"Melee / Natural Weapon Stuck: Make a damage roll for the attack. The result is the Strength (Base HTH damage) roll needed to dislodge the weapon. Each attempt takes the character's entire Movement phase.  (Default: 9)","weight":1,"range":[13,14],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":13,"rangeH":14},{"_id":"3jLcsbt2vuQcoDgw","type":0,"text":"Lost Opportunity: The attacker loses the rest of their turn.  (Default: 17)","weight":1,"range":[15,16],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":15,"rangeH":16},{"_id":"oOSbjBgThVx7ub7m","type":0,"text":"Gear Damage: If the attacker has any breakable gear, select one piece at random. Roll their Base HTH Damage and compare the result to the Gear’s Breakpoint to see if it breaks.  (Default: 19)","weight":1,"range":[17,18],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":17,"rangeH":18},{"_id":"GG5dbhRUpo3tDZR1","type":0,"text":"Other: The GM may create a critical result appropriate to the situation, or else roll twice again and combine the results.","weight":1,"range":[19,20],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":19,"rangeH":20}],"formula":"d20","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"22naRhe7LCeAQWCZ":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"RollTable.pbt9WxRpbe4yQNJE"}},"_id":"5cusW4pHaskZ0raA"}
{"name":"Critical Success","img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","description":"Roll the outcome of a successful critical hit","results":[{"_id":"F0MTS17tSXz2TgRO","type":0,"text":"Gear Shot: If the target has any breakable Gear, one piece of Gear (selected at random) is hit. Compare the damage result to the gear’s Breakpoint to see if it breaks. If the Gear doesn’t break, then the character still suffers the full effect of the attack.  (Default: 12)","weight":1,"range":[1,2],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":1,"rangeH":2},{"_id":"l4jfIx0N7s7VuMnR","type":0,"text":"Free Action: The attacker gets another action after this one is resolved, without suffering any additional Multiple Action penalties.  (Default: 19)","weight":1,"range":[3,4],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":3,"rangeH":4},{"_id":"3F6xMiP7DQJF5PfX","type":0,"text":"Leg Shot: The attack strikes the target in a randomly selected leg. See Called Shots (see 4.14.2).  (Default: 15)","weight":1,"range":[5,6],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":5,"rangeH":6},{"_id":"kCld7AR1Hcbk9a9q","type":0,"text":"Avoid Light Armor: If the target has Armor (or any similar protective Ability), and that Ability offers only Light Partial Coverage, this attack strikes the target in an unprotected spot. This result also avoids Light Cover.  (Default: 15)","weight":1,"range":[7,7],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":7,"rangeH":7},{"_id":"meIaYzQXbHZFlzdJ","type":0,"text":"Avoid Armor: If the target has Armor (or any similar protective Ability), and that Ability offers only Partial Coverage (Light OR Heavy), the attack strikes the target in an unprotected spot. This result also avoids Light or Heavy Cover.  (Default: 15)","weight":1,"range":[8,8],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":8,"rangeH":8},{"_id":"7fQl1t8QmjRpKKHx","type":0,"text":"Muscle Strain: The target strains themself. Roll the target’s Base HTH damage, divide by 2, and round up. Their protection applies against this damage, and they may roll with it.  (Default: 15)","weight":1,"range":[9,9],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":9,"rangeH":9},{"_id":"5sSpJffw336uE7dg","type":0,"text":"Arm Shot: The attack strikes the target in a randomly selected arm. See Called Shots (see 4.14.2).  (Default: 15)","weight":1,"range":[10,11],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":10,"rangeH":11},{"_id":"fzefqKJ3CUF0NwyV","type":0,"text":"Precise Hit: The amount of damage the target can roll with from this attack is halved (rounded down).  (Default: 15)","weight":1,"range":[12,13],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":12,"rangeH":13},{"_id":"3jLcsbt2vuQcoDgw","type":0,"text":"Solid Hit: Add 3 to the damage roll (or add 3 to a Grapnel’s breakpoint, etc.). If the attack is a non-damage based Ability which requires a save, subtract 3 from the target’s saving roll target number.","weight":1,"range":[14,15],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":14,"rangeH":15},{"_id":"oOSbjBgThVx7ub7m","type":0,"text":"Off Balance: The defender suffers a penalty of -3 on defense until they regain their balance on their next turn.  (Default: 15)","weight":1,"range":[16,17],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":16,"rangeH":17},{"_id":"322UelYMfq7AKQUc","type":0,"text":"Head Shot: The attack strikes the target in the head. See Called Shots (see 4.14.2).  (Default: 15)","weight":1,"range":[18,18],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":18,"rangeH":18},{"_id":"GG5dbhRUpo3tDZR1","type":0,"text":"Other: The GM may create a critical result appropriate to the situation, or else roll twice again and combine the results.","weight":1,"range":[19,20],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","rangeL":19,"rangeH":20}],"formula":"d20","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"22naRhe7LCeAQWCZ":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"RollTable.FJ9S3bxFpdOzj3pY"}},"_id":"pjXTunngXcc3tqgB"}
